WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.389
Hey, good morning family. I'm excited to

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:04.309
be with you all again today.

00:00:04.319 --> 00:00:07.190
I've taken some time to pray and I've

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:10.350
been seeking the Lord about 2024.

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:16.230
I don't take this lightly, speaking

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:18.910
to you all like this and telling you

00:00:18.920 --> 00:00:21.990
all what's coming and

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:23.830
warning you about the Father's Heart

00:00:23.830 --> 00:00:23.840
and

00:00:23.840 --> 00:00:25.390
what's going on in the

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:28.710
spirit realm. Like I said,

00:00:28.720 --> 00:00:30.150
I've just been taking some time

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:32.630
seeking Him, getting into the Word more,

00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:35.229
and not allowing all the

00:00:35.239 --> 00:00:38.709
pressure of life to try to squash out

00:00:38.719 --> 00:00:42.549
the voice. This has been a trip

00:00:42.559 --> 00:00:45.270
for me. I just started

00:00:45.280 --> 00:00:48.950
this YouTube channel in March, and it's

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:51.229
been like a fire hose the last couple of

00:00:51.239 --> 00:00:54.110
weeks with all the stuff

00:00:54.110 --> 00:00:54.120
coming—not

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:58.310
necessarily always

00:00:58.320 --> 00:01:01.549
good. I just

00:01:01.559 --> 00:01:03.069
want to take some time; I have a hard

00:01:03.079 --> 00:01:06.749
word to give again.

00:01:08.759 --> 00:01:11.190
I'm going to say it like this: the

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:13.149
Lord's called me to say the hard things,

00:01:13.159 --> 00:01:17.510
y'all, and it's not always easy being me.

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:19.950
But I'm going to tell you

00:01:19.960 --> 00:01:22.230
exactly what's going on regardless of

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:25.390
all this other crap you're hearing on

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:27.190
the other platforms. That's what I'm

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:30.069
going to tell you: it's pure crap. After

00:01:30.079 --> 00:01:32.149
sitting before the Father last

00:01:32.159 --> 00:01:35.910
night and getting the download that I

00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:38.510
got, I hope you all still stick

00:01:38.520 --> 00:01:40.670
around because I'm going to tell you the

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:43.469
truth about what's coming, and you all need

00:01:43.479 --> 00:01:47.230
to hear it. So here it goes. I was

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:51.149
praying before, just like I always

00:01:51.159 --> 00:01:55.350
do, and I felt the heaviness

00:01:55.360 --> 00:01:57.510
coming on

00:01:57.520 --> 00:02:00.429
me. It was

00:02:00.439 --> 00:02:02.910
very intense intercessory

00:02:02.920 --> 00:02:05.029
prayer, and all of a sudden, I know when

00:02:05.039 --> 00:02:07.389
the Lord's about to speak now because I

00:02:07.399 --> 00:02:09.109
feel it; it's like a bubble

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:12.110
up inside of me prophetically.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:15.390
So I told my son, 'Get the recorder

00:02:15.400 --> 00:02:17.150
out right now because I don't want to forget

00:02:17.160 --> 00:02:19.390
anything He's going to

00:02:19.400 --> 00:02:22.750
talk about.'All of a sudden, the Word of the

00:02:22.760 --> 00:02:24.710
Lord came up to me and I saw a

00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:27.710
vision.

00:02:37.640 --> 00:02:42.350
I saw preachers standing behind the pulpits. Holy Spirit, I ask you to deliver it just the way you

00:02:42.350 --> 00:02:42.360
delivered it the first time. Thank you. I saw preachers standing behind the

00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:45.830
pulpit and they had oil—this smooth, oily-looking

00:02:45.830 --> 00:02:45.840
oil—all

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:48.910
over their

00:02:48.910 --> 00:02:48.920
mouths

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:53.149
and it was dripping from their

00:02:53.159 --> 00:02:57.470
lips. They had roaches and bugs

00:02:57.480 --> 00:03:00.070
crawling in and out of their mouths and

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:03.910
laying upon their lips. Bugs

00:03:03.920 --> 00:03:05.949
were crawling in their teeth and

00:03:05.959 --> 00:03:07.589
in and out of their

00:03:07.589 --> 00:03:07.599
mouths

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:10.110
and they would lay upon their lips

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:11.270
as they would

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:15.509
speak. They had a

00:03:15.509 --> 00:03:15.519
shrewdness

00:03:15.519 --> 00:03:19.470
in their eyes; their

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:22.190
motives behind what they were preaching

00:03:22.190 --> 00:03:22.200
were

00:03:22.200 --> 00:03:24.390
all

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:26.630
selfish

00:03:26.640 --> 00:03:30.190
gain, trying to appease the ear of the

00:03:30.200 --> 00:03:33.589
people. Then I saw ears on the people, and

00:03:33.599 --> 00:03:36.550
I could see their ears were just being pacified

00:03:36.550 --> 00:03:36.560
by all

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:40.030
these whispers of the

00:03:40.040 --> 00:03:41.789
things that were happening in the spirit:

00:03:44.159 --> 00:03:46.270
'Everything is going to be good; all

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:47.830
things are going to work for your

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:49.229
good for those that love the

00:03:49.229 --> 00:03:49.239
Lord.'They

00:03:49.239 --> 00:03:51.070
were speaking the Word, but they

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:53.750
were not speaking what was on God's

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:56.750
heart. They were speaking things, but they

00:03:56.760 --> 00:03:59.830
weren't speaking things to make you grow.

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:02.509
I saw these

00:04:02.519 --> 00:04:04.789
bugs coming out of their teeth and

00:04:04.799 --> 00:04:05.869
out of their mouths,

00:04:05.869 --> 00:04:05.879
and

00:04:05.879 --> 00:04:09.830
I looked across

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.270
the land of

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:14.509
America. There were babies with

00:04:14.519 --> 00:04:18.229
diapers on all throughout the land. There

00:04:18.239 --> 00:04:21.670
was nobody with backbone. They were all

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:23.430
like really

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:26.070
lethargic babies that had diapers

00:04:26.070 --> 00:04:26.080
on—these

00:04:26.080 --> 00:04:28.990
Pampers. I saw,

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:32.270
whenever you see soiled diapers, the smell

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:34.870
that rises up like in cartoons.

00:04:37.479 --> 00:04:40.830
All the babies had soiled diapers

00:04:40.840 --> 00:04:43.070
on and there were flies buzzing around

00:04:43.080 --> 00:04:46.230
those babies. The babies were crying,

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:52.189
'Please, change my

00:04:52.189 --> 00:04:52.199
diaper!'There

00:04:52.199 --> 00:04:54.990
were literally thousands

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:57.230
and thousands and thousands of babies

00:04:57.240 --> 00:05:00.790
full of dirty diapers, and the preachers

00:05:00.800 --> 00:05:03.189
were not teaching

00:05:03.199 --> 00:05:05.629
them. The Lord spoke to me and he

00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:08.270
said,

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:10.590
'Brandon, the preachers are not

00:05:10.600 --> 00:05:13.510
teaching the milk or the meat of the word to

00:05:13.520 --> 00:05:17.790
grow my children up into adult

00:05:17.790 --> 00:05:17.800
stature.'He

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:21.469
said, 'Therefore,

00:05:21.479 --> 00:05:24.590
there is going to be a great shifting

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:28.629
upon the land.'He said,

00:05:28.639 --> 00:05:31.510
'They have raised their

00:05:31.520 --> 00:05:34.309
noses towards me with a stiff

00:05:34.309 --> 00:05:34.319
neck.'Their

00:05:34.319 --> 00:05:37.110
noses were pointed up

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:40.510
towards God. I saw a pride that was upon

00:05:40.520 --> 00:05:43.430
the people. He said, 'There's a pride

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:47.029
upon the people and they have a stench

00:05:47.039 --> 00:05:50.749
before me. Therefore, what is coming... there

00:05:50.749 --> 00:05:50.759
are

00:05:50.759 --> 00:05:53.550
prophecies going forth

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:56.230
about a great revival, about a great

00:05:56.240 --> 00:05:58.510
harvest, about all these things, but

00:05:58.520 --> 00:06:00.670
judgment comes in the house of the

00:06:00.680 --> 00:06:04.350
Lord first. Therefore, there will be a

00:06:04.360 --> 00:06:08.189
great shifting take place and there will

00:06:08.199 --> 00:06:11.070
be what people call a

00:06:11.080 --> 00:06:14.070
great Ichabod come upon the

00:06:14.070 --> 00:06:14.080
land.'He

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:17.589
said, 'I have told you this before,

00:06:17.599 --> 00:06:20.550
but there will be a great Ichabod come

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:22.710
upon the land.'It would

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:25.230
seem like it, but I will never leave you

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:28.189
and I will never leave nor will I

00:06:28.189 --> 00:06:28.199
forsake

00:06:28.199 --> 00:06:31.830
you. But there will be a shifting,

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:36.150
and he said a shaking is coming to the Body.

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:42.670
I saw a sluice box, the kind

00:06:42.670 --> 00:06:42.680
that sifts

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:45.430
dirt

00:06:45.440 --> 00:06:49.309
from the gold, and I saw

00:06:49.319 --> 00:06:52.309
this manure, dirt, and all

00:06:52.319 --> 00:06:56.550
this debris inside this box.

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:59.110
He said, 'You have to shift the

00:06:59.110 --> 00:06:59.120
box.'He

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:01.909
showed me Him sifting

00:07:01.919 --> 00:07:05.869
the box and shaking it so the gold

00:07:05.869 --> 00:07:05.879
rises

00:07:05.879 --> 00:07:08.790
to the top and the dirt

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:11.469
was falling to the ground.

00:07:11.479 --> 00:07:14.230
But it comes through a great

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:17.110
shaking. He said, 'You have to shake all

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:19.790
the debris and all the stuff off so that

00:07:19.800 --> 00:07:21.150
the gold will

00:07:21.150 --> 00:07:21.160
rise.'Then

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:23.749
he said, 'I want you to

00:07:23.759 --> 00:07:27.270
focus on the great sequoia tree out in

00:07:27.270 --> 00:07:27.280
California.'He

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:29.629
said, 'I want you to

00:07:29.629 --> 00:07:29.639
focus.'He

00:07:29.639 --> 00:07:34.430
said, 'The seed does not produce

00:07:34.440 --> 00:07:38.150
until there is great fire upon it, and it

00:07:38.160 --> 00:07:40.670
will be released when there is fire

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:43.550
upon it.'He said, 'You will be like the

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:46.070
great sequoia tree that grows its roots

00:07:46.080 --> 00:07:50.430
down deep.'I saw a

00:07:50.440 --> 00:07:53.189
fire coming upon the land, but it was

00:07:53.199 --> 00:07:56.670
like a refiner's

00:07:56.670 --> 00:07:56.680
fire—not

00:07:56.680 --> 00:08:00.629
a physical fire, but a refiner's fire.

00:08:00.639 --> 00:08:03.189
I saw the refiner's fire burning upon

00:08:03.199 --> 00:08:05.909
the seed and all of a sudden, the ground

00:08:05.919 --> 00:08:09.270
from as far

00:08:09.280 --> 00:08:11.589
as the eye could see was completely

00:08:11.599 --> 00:08:15.350
charred, tested by fire. In this

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:21.230
'tested by fire,'then I saw new growth, new

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:24.589
green grass growing because

00:08:24.599 --> 00:08:27.350
the weeds and all the stuff were burnt up.

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:30.510
I saw green, new flowers,

00:08:30.520 --> 00:08:34.029
beautiful new things coming. I

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:37.909
saw those sequoia plants being

00:08:37.919 --> 00:08:40.870
planted and growing up because of the

00:08:40.880 --> 00:08:42.670
fire and the testing that was coming

00:08:42.680 --> 00:08:46.150
upon the people. The Lord told

00:08:46.160 --> 00:08:50.430
me, he showed me... like I

00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:53.310
tell you all, I see calendars sometimes

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:56.070
and he shows me things like in windows

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:59.430
of time. I saw a time of testing

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:03.470
coming. I saw times of hardship coming

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:07.550
upon the people. I saw the glorious

00:09:07.560 --> 00:09:12.310
church rising in a window

00:09:12.320 --> 00:09:16.750
of time with great glory. I saw an

00:09:16.760 --> 00:09:18.870
outpouring of the spirit of God and

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:21.910
healings and manifestations of the glory

00:09:21.920 --> 00:09:26.030
beyond anybody's

00:09:26.040 --> 00:09:28.350
comprehension. But he said the church is

00:09:28.360 --> 00:09:31.990
not ready for this. He said, 'There

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:34.190
must be holiness and

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:36.030
righteousness preached back in the

00:09:36.040 --> 00:09:39.470
pulpits to shake the people, to teach

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:41.630
them how to stand on the meat of the

00:09:41.640 --> 00:09:44.550
word, not on the milk of the word.'There

00:09:44.550 --> 00:09:44.560
are

00:09:44.560 --> 00:09:47.509
too many babies and therefore there will

00:09:47.519 --> 00:09:50.550
be a great shaking coming. Like I

00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:54.550
said, then all of a sudden I saw people

00:09:54.560 --> 00:09:57.350
that he said, 'You

00:09:57.360 --> 00:10:00.910
call me Lord, Lord. You call me savior. You

00:10:00.920 --> 00:10:03.910
call me your friend.'He said, 'I do not

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:07.230
know you, for your heart is far from

00:10:07.230 --> 00:10:07.240
me.'He

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:10.829
said,

00:10:10.839 --> 00:10:14.030
'Just like Peter that said he

00:10:14.040 --> 00:10:17.150
would never deny me, he denied me

00:10:17.160 --> 00:10:19.710
three times.'Therefore, there will be

00:10:19.720 --> 00:10:22.190
a lot of you that, just when pressure

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:24.949
comes and these great trials

00:10:24.949 --> 00:10:24.959
come—as

00:10:24.959 --> 00:10:26.710
the shiftings and

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:29.350
the refining fire comes on them—he said,

00:10:29.360 --> 00:10:31.230
'You have called me Lord, Lord,

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:33.590
but you will deny me three times just

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:36.750
like Peter did.'He said

00:10:36.760 --> 00:10:39.230
there will be a great shifting in this

00:10:39.240 --> 00:10:40.829
and a great

00:10:40.839 --> 00:10:43.470
falling away for the ones that call me

00:10:43.480 --> 00:10:45.829
Lord, Lord, but never really truly made me Lord

00:10:45.839 --> 00:10:48.310
of their life and made me savior over

00:10:48.320 --> 00:10:50.829
them. Therefore, those who rise up

00:10:50.839 --> 00:10:53.590
out of that fire

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:56.269
and that refining, he

00:10:56.279 --> 00:10:58.509
said they are the ones that

00:10:58.519 --> 00:11:01.629
will have boldness to walk before me

00:11:01.639 --> 00:11:04.629
in these end times. 'Did I not say in my

00:11:04.629 --> 00:11:04.639
word,'he

00:11:04.639 --> 00:11:07.949
said, 'that in the end many

00:11:07.959 --> 00:11:10.990
will come to me saying, "Did I not

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:13.310
prophesy in your name? Did I not lay

00:11:13.320 --> 00:11:15.670
hands on the sick in your name? Did I not

00:11:15.680 --> 00:11:18.550
cast out devils in your

00:11:18.550 --> 00:11:18.560
name?"'and

00:11:18.560 --> 00:11:21.670
he said, 'Depart from me, I never knew

00:11:21.670 --> 00:11:21.680
you.'Those

00:11:21.680 --> 00:11:25.350
scriptures are true and they

00:11:25.360 --> 00:11:27.670
are alive and they are going forth, and

00:11:27.680 --> 00:11:30.990
this will happen. Do you

00:11:31.000 --> 00:11:33.910
understand? Those were prophecies that

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:36.990
God spoke before

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:39.509
the beginning of time. Look at the words

00:11:39.519 --> 00:11:43.150
that are coming to pass: all men's hearts

00:11:43.160 --> 00:11:45.389
will fail them for fear for what's

00:11:45.399 --> 00:11:47.269
coming upon the earth. They will be lovers

00:11:47.269 --> 00:11:47.279
of themselves.

00:11:47.279 --> 00:11:50.550
It is coming

00:11:50.560 --> 00:11:53.350
upon the land even more—even

00:11:53.350 --> 00:11:53.360
a

00:11:53.360 --> 00:11:56.509
greater loving of self. They have

00:11:56.519 --> 00:11:58.949
itching ears. Their hearts

00:11:58.959 --> 00:12:02.110
are full of gall

00:12:02.110 --> 00:12:02.120
and

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:04.990
evilness. But the Lord says

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:08.030
he's bringing forth a refiner's fire, and

00:12:08.040 --> 00:12:11.190
many will say it is a great Ichabod. Many

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:13.509
will say what's coming is a great

00:12:13.509 --> 00:12:13.519
Ichabod,

00:12:13.519 --> 00:12:17.550
but it is not an Ichabod; it is refining.

00:12:17.560 --> 00:12:19.990
Like I said, I'm not coming on

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:22.550
here to give you an itching ear word

00:12:22.560 --> 00:12:24.990
today to tell you everything is always

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:27.829
going to be good for some folks, but I'm

00:12:27.839 --> 00:12:29.389
going to tell you: if you're walking with

00:12:29.399 --> 00:12:32.550
the Lord right now,

00:12:32.560 --> 00:12:34.949
you'll lack nothing. Everything will

00:12:34.959 --> 00:12:36.990
always be okay with you if you are

00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:38.430
already walking with Him, if you're

00:12:38.440 --> 00:12:40.150
walking through that refiner's fire, if

00:12:40.160 --> 00:12:42.189
you're standing

00:12:42.199 --> 00:12:44.150
before Him righteous and listening to

00:12:44.160 --> 00:12:46.150
Him every day and praying and seeking

00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:49.310
His face daily and reading His word and

00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:52.189
having fellowship with Him.

00:12:52.199 --> 00:12:54.590
The Word said, 'I'll never see the

00:12:54.600 --> 00:12:58.310
righteous forsaken or his seed begging

00:12:58.310 --> 00:12:58.320
bread.'Think

00:12:58.320 --> 00:13:00.750
about what He's saying.

00:13:00.760 --> 00:13:02.750
Many of you say, 'Well, I'm

00:13:02.750 --> 00:13:02.760
righteous.'No,

00:13:02.760 --> 00:13:05.150
you're not; you're walking in

00:13:05.150 --> 00:13:05.160
compromise.

00:13:05.160 --> 00:13:07.790
I'm coming to tell you

00:13:07.800 --> 00:13:09.870
there's a lot of you that are babies,

00:13:09.880 --> 00:13:11.870
just like he told me, and the babies are

00:13:11.880 --> 00:13:14.509
upon the land. The preachers have

00:13:14.519 --> 00:13:18.949
been preaching you a smooth,

00:13:18.959 --> 00:13:21.509
oily,

00:13:21.509 --> 00:13:21.519
roach-filled

00:13:21.519 --> 00:13:23.910
word; they aren't teaching you how to

00:13:23.920 --> 00:13:26.110
stand. You come to this channel and I'm

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:28.949
